Invocation Name: universal freemason
des: Listen to the latest podcast from Universal Freemason Research Society as your rambling host deciphers Masonic philosophies from Masonic authors such as Manly P. Hall, Albert G. Mackey, Albert Pike, John J. Robinson and many others! You can ask ALEXA to shuffle podcast episodes or play in any order! Nothing to buy, no solicitation to join any Masonic lodge, just purely discovery new ideas from a Freemason point of view. OPEN TO EVERYONE LOOKING FOR NEW POINTS OF VIEW OR INTERESTED IN MASONIC PHILOSOPHIES.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
